        private void determineFinalAttributeSet(java.util.Vector treatedUnits)
        Find clusters of units that meet the minimum aggregate acres. Once found remove random clusters of units from treated lists until we meet the maximum treated acres requirement.
        Parameters:
        treatedUnits - list of units to potentially treat.
